OL,3,CMost Blue Islands' customers should
OL,4,Cget money back, says travel expert
OL,6,FMost Blue Islands' passengers left
OL,7,Fwith voided tickets for future flights
OL,8,Fcan expect to be refunded, according
OL,9,Fto a top travel expert.
OL,11,FSimon Calder has reassured those who
OL,12,Fbooked directly with the collapsed
OL,13,Fairline that "it should generally be
OL,14,Fvery easy to retrieve the cash" if
OL,15,Fthey paid by either credit or debit
OL,16,Fcard.
