OL,3,CMost Blue Islands' customers should
OL,4,Cget money back, says travel expert
OL,6,FThe financial impact is especially
OL,7,Fharsh for frequent fliers and sports
OL,8,Fclubs, some of whom had bulk-booked
OL,9,Fthousands of pounds worth of services
OL,10,Fto secure the best rates.
OL,12,FHowever, Mr Calder says there is a
OL,13,Fgood chance of them getting their
OL,14,Fmoney back.
OL,16,FHe explains: "Many people will simply
OL,17,Fhave booked direct using a credit card
OL,18,For a debit card, and on debit cards
OL,19,Fthere's something called a chargeback,
OL,20,Fwhich is basically the same thing you
OL,21,Fget with a credit card.
