OL,3,CMost Blue Islands' customers should
OL,4,Cget money back, says travel expert
OL,6,FThis means that when a credit card is
OL,7,Fused to pay more than #100 for goods
OL,8,Fand services which were not delivered,
OL,9,For the firm providing them went bust,
OL,10,Fthe card provider is jointly liable
OL,11,Fwith the supplier and should provide a
OL,12,Ffull refund.
OL,14,FFor those who used a Mastercard or
OL,15,FVisa debit card, similar cover exists
OL,16,Fthrough a chargeback scheme to the
OL,17,Fcard issuer or bank.
