OL,3,CMost Blue Islands' customers should
OL,4,Cget money back, says travel expert
OL,6,FIt allows customers to cancel
OL,7,Ftransactions if problems occur, and
OL,8,Funlike credit cards is not limited to
OL,9,Fpurchases of #100 or more, but does
OL,10,Fhave time limits of as little as 120
OL,11,Fdays to apply.
OL,13,FTo claim this back, a Negative
OL,14,FResponse Letter from the aviation
OL,15,Fauthorities is usually needed to
OL,16,Fconfirm that Blue Islands has ceased
OL,17,Foperating.
