OL,3,CMost Blue Islands' customers should
OL,4,Cget money back, says travel expert
OL,6,FThis does not exist yet, as Blue
OL,7,FIslands has not been declared
OL,8,Finsolvent, but liquidators have now
OL,9,Fbeen appointed.
OL,11,FThe company's statement may be enough
OL,12,Fto substantiate a refund claim with a
OL,13,Fcredit or debit card provider,
OL,14,FJersey's Consumer Council says.
OL,16,FHowever, Mr Calder has warned that
OL,17,Fcustomers who booked through a third
OL,18,Fparty may face a more complex process
OL,19,Fto get their money back.
